name: Pnut's Dog
description: This project revolves around Tucker, the friend of Peanut the Squirrel, a widely recognized social media figure and rescue animal. Peanut was seized by the New York State Department of Environmental Conservation due to concerns about the legality of keeping wildlife as pets and potential health risks. Subsequently, Peanut was euthanized, leading to widespread public outcry and significant media coverage. Source: https://www.instagram.com/reel/C4g-DkAuiRK/
